The rate was reasonable, but the room was small and the bathroom and shower smaller still.	Our room was basic but comfortable, had a great shower and was lovely to watch the world pass by out of our window.	Our room was not the largest, but for two people who just need a place to sleep and shower, it was perfect.	Although our room was rather small, it was clean and neat, the bed was very wide and comfortable and there were enough place in wardrobe for all our stuff.	The room was small (like any other in the city), but we comfortably stayed in a triple room.